# UI: shadcn/ui + TenantShield theme

## Component strategy (order)

1. **Reuse** primitives under `@/components/ui` (see `components.json`).
2. **If missing** from the shadcn registry: `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add <component>`.
3. **One-off UI**: implement inline in the page/feature with React + Tailwind + **theme tokens**. Do not add shared components for tiny markup.

Extract a component only when reused heavily or state grows.

## `app/globals.css` is the single source of truth

Use **only shadcn semantic tokens** — no parallel custom color layers (`cream-*`, `ink-warm`, `surface-strong`, etc.).

- **No** ad-hoc hex/HSL or raw palette utilities (`bg-zinc-900`, `text-amber-300`) for product UI.
- **Do** use tokens exposed via `@theme inline` and `:root` / `.dark`.

### Semantic token map

| Purpose | Token / class |
|---------|---------------|
| Page canvas | `bg-background`, `text-foreground` |
| Elevated cards / list rows | `bg-card`, `text-card-foreground`, `border-border` |
| Inputs / dropdowns | `bg-popover`, `border-input`, `ring-ring` |
| Orange accent (gauge, badges, plan card) | `bg-primary`, `text-primary` |
| Soft fills (icon boxes, note boxes) | `bg-accent`, `text-accent-foreground` |
| Secondary text / eyebrows | `text-muted-foreground` |
| Subtle surface tint | `bg-muted` |
| Dark hero / featured tile / black CTA | `bg-foreground`, `text-background` |
| Primary orange button | `Button variant="default"` |
| Black pill CTA | `Button variant="cta"` → `bg-foreground text-background` |
| Feedback | `text-destructive`, `bg-destructive`, `text-warning`, `bg-warning` |

Light/dark: extend **only** in `globals.css` (`:root` / `.dark` + `@theme inline` when adding a new `--color-*`). Do not add parallel color systems in TS or random CSS files.

Loader animations (`gavel-*`, `shield-*` vars) live in loader CSS files only — not in the app theme.

## Examples

```tsx
// ✅ Cream page + dark hero card
<main className="bg-background">
  <section className="rounded-3xl bg-foreground p-5 text-background">…</section>
</main>

// ✅ White list row
<Card className="border-border bg-card">…</Card>

// ✅ Black CTA
<Button variant="cta" className="h-12 w-full rounded-full">Sign In</Button>

// ✅ Auth inputs
<Input className="border-border bg-popover" />

// ❌ Avoid
<div className="bg-cream-page text-ink-warm border-cream-border" />
<div className="bg-[#f5f0e8] text-[#1a1a1a]" />
```

Match existing patterns: Radix + `cn()` + `class-variance-authority` in `@/components/ui`.
